# Summary
This documentation details the integration between Segment and Amplitude, covering setup options including client-side bundled integration and Segment destinations/sources configuration. It explains the mapping between Segment and Amplitude SDK functions, cohort export capabilities, and the advantages of using Amplitude's native SDKs alongside Segment for enhanced session tracking and user property collection.

